            Automated programming and scheduling delivers parts in 24 hours or less
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Fair Pricing -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-purple-600">üíé</div>
